channel.title: Project Revolution 474 [FINAL]
channel.description:
[center][b]Welcome to the offical Project Revolution 474 thread.[/b][/center] [center]Project Revolution is a Project Insanity based server.[/center]
[b]About myself:[/b] Hey Moparian's, Let me introduce myself. My name is Christopher and I'm a fairly new member of this community, I'm 16 years old and I live in Australia. This is my second time posting a thread on these forums so please bare with me. I'm new to coding and I hate following tutorials, I like to do things myself and making them the best way possible.
[b]About this project:[/b] It's a more stable, bug free, eco friendly, better looking and easy to code PI source. It's ready to host right away or to start another project with.
Features I added during the Pre-Beta:
[ul][li]Removed all possible dupes.[/li] [li]Rare drop spam when running the server has been removed.[/li] [li]Fixed deadlocks.[/li] [li]Redone commands.java.[/li] [li]Fixed PM issues.[/li] [li]Improved a few methods.[/li] [li]Fixed 2 ranged with 99 magic and 9 combat level glitch.[/li] [li]Fixed all the 800 warnings eclipse gives you.[/li] [li]Fixed ClanChat.[/li] [li]Redone Jad. (1 Wave)[/li] [li]No need to log out when you enter Fight Caves.[/li] [li]Fixed God Wars npc's.[/li] [li]Redone shops.[/li] [li]Removed Giles at home.[/li] [li]Added alters at home.[/li] [li]Fixed Lunar magic book freezing.[/li] [li]Fixed veng spell.[/li] [li]Cleaned out quest tab.[/li] [li]Added ::Commands[/li] [li]Added ::Rules[/li] [li]Added ::MB (Mage Bank Tele)[/li] [li]Redone Barrows.java[/li] [li]New crowns.[/li] [li]Removed all of Sanity's exploits.[/li] [li]Redone CombatAssistant.java[/li] [li]Cleaned Client.java[/li][/ul]
A few pictures from the Public Pre-Beta Server: [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/SKb79.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/AgmPH.png[/img]
[b]More pictures and information is on the Pre-Beta thread: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,567153.0.html Download Link For "Project Revolution 474 [Final Beta]: http://www.mirrorfile.com/4ywflk2gm429 I plan to release the open source and open client on the 1st of March 2013, If you need it before then please leave me a E-Mail at: contact.christopherdsouza@gmail.com or add me on Skype: Chriiss2012.[/b]
